title: From "Diet or Die" to Soulja Boy's Lie
itunes:title: From "Diet or Die" to Soulja Boy's Lie
description:
MON 5/23 - Dr. Natasha Sandy joins The Breakfast Club to help kick-start your weight loss program and Envy, Angela & Charlamagne agree to pay for 2 listeners to get healthy! Wonder if they'll be using some of Soulja Boy's $400 million to pay for that? Oh, it's not $400 million...? Let's discuss.
